{
  "stem": "9446.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You had to use a crank and-- and in order to start the ignition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was the way the tractor operated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Except a tractor is a lot heavier machine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So if you get, like, premature ignition, the club goes, the crank goes back, and can kill you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it almost did in my case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was what I had to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I had to run this tractor machine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They taught me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a special class.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was pretty good at  it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At least running the tractor gave me an opportunity to have some more bread, because what we were doing, it was like a stationary machine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't go anywhere with this tractor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were milling, you know, like when you have a  mill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You make flour.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that machine was connected with the other machine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the tractor's engine was running it-- you know what I mean-- and creating flour, milling, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was like a milling machine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Like-- So that was my job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had to sit there all day and watch the tractor [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I even had a job, once, which was considered a miracle, for about three or four weeks, in a bakery.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In time of war, when people were starving to death, working in a bakery, surrounded by all-- by all that bread was being in a paradise.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could eat all you wanted while you there, but you were not allowed to take   a crumb of bread out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they catch you taking a slice of bread, they kill you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the moment-- the way things happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, while you're there, you see all the bread around you, and you're not hungry.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
